<div class="wh-start">
  <div class="wh-logo"></div>
  <h1>How should we set up your site?</h1>

  <div class="wy-alert wy-alert-info">
    <div class="wy-alert-title">Heads up alpha users... pick the option on the right!</div>
    <p>
      We don't have any useful themes currently, but they do work if you wanted to make your own.
      Themes are just a sites <code>pages</code>, <code>templates</code> and <code>static</code> directories
      bundled into a zip file. Check the <a href="">documentation page here</a> for more information.
    </p>
  </div>

  <section>
    <center>
      <h4>Show me some magic.</h4>
      <img src="http://cms.webhook.com/v1/assets/images/wizard.png"/>
      {{#link-to 'theme' class="btn btn-neutral icon icon-rocket"}} Start from a theme{{/link-to}}
    </center>
    <hr/>
    <p>
      Pick one of our pre-built sites that follow common
      CMS and design patterns. Customize later.
    </p>
    <p>
      Example: A blog site, a portfolio site.
    </p>
  </section>
  <section class="wh-start-or">
    Or
  </section>
  <section>
    <center>
      <h4>I am the magic!</h4>
      <img src="http://cms.webhook.com/v1/assets/images/dragon.png"/>
      {{#link-to 'wh.content.all-types' class="btn btn-neutral icon icon-leaf"}} Start from scratch{{/link-to}}
    </center>
    <hr/>
    <p>
      Use the formbuilder to set up a custom CMS with
      page types that you define.
    </p>
    <p>You'll need to code your design in HTML / CSS.</p>
  </section>
</div>
